<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Advert Published</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h2>Advert Published</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>We are pleased to inform you that your advert titled "<strong>{{ advert.title }}</strong>" has been successfully published on our platform.</p>
        <p>Description of the advert:</p>
        <blockquote>
            {{ advert.context }}
        </blockquote>
        <p>You can view your advert by clicking on the following link:</p>
        <p><a href="{{ url('app_advert_show', {'id': advert.id}) }}">View the Advert</a></p>
        <p>Thank you for using our service!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply directly.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

